{"tid":1465791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再割咪再鬧啦咁多位手足","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:01.000Z","uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b62fa3d980f66e14f7f5395db5116327ac20321c","tid":1465791,"uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"今晚機場一事引左好多好多手足內鬥<br />\n老實講好冇益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都係本住五大訴求<br />\n大家都係想香港好<br />\n但衣加就開口埋口P牌仔分化撚<br />\n今晚對我嚟講係呢兩個月抗爭嘅小失敗<br />\n影響左旅客影響左人地對我地嘅觀感<br />\n但係呢個時候我地竟然唔係反思檢討有咩地方改善<br />\n而係不斷話人係鬼係分化撚<br />\n咁對成個運動係冇幫助仲要踩自己友幾腳<br />\n只係一件好小好小嘅分歧<br />\n其實根本冇需要亦都冇時間俾我地去鬧自己人<br />\n再鬧落去咪同雨革一樣分裂收場<br />\n衣加要做嘅係諗更好嘅方法<br />\n勇武同和理非雙管齊下先有用<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n勇武同和理非都一樣<br />\n就算警察有臥底<br />\n我地都唔可以因為咁而猜度自己人<br />\n我諗香港人一定可以connect<br />\n記住 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">We Connect</span></span>"},{"pid":"b72fe2432600a079f241506d051bbf89bbb6e8b3","tid":1465791,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"梁天琦：懇請不要被仇恨支配自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請各位機場手足唔好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地啦 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好衝動啊 求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c40c4e092b1c90e17ca2fea1d9fc203e6e812a","tid":1465791,"uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割</span>"},{"pid":"b8e0b57391884954cdfa4c8a5095a70fc4e3e2ea","tid":1465791,"uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span>"},{"pid":"615469fb9f546435666a81042e5071ef8139ce62","tid":1465791,"uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span>"},{"pid":"3fb4c1cb471c4fbfe0ac3ff1f013479252b964ec","tid":1465791,"uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span>"},{"pid":"fd7f04204916455f6175e145eaf8eb92baad8179","tid":1465791,"uid":205857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"<span s